          "bandits",
          "Boulderfall border"
        ],
        "type": "KNOWLEDGE"
      },
      {
        "always_inject": false,
        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownWindhelmFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionWindhelm\")",
        "content": "Steamcrag Camp is a giant encampment south of Windhelm in Eastmarch, with mammoths grazing on the slopes around the hot springs. The giants don't trouble travelers who don't trouble them.",
        "display_name": "Steamcrag Camp",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.55,
        "knowledge_key": "dungeon.eastmarch.steamcrag_camp",
        "location": "",
        "tags": [
          "Steamcrag Camp",
          "giant camp",
          "Eastmarch",
          "hot springs",
          "mammoths"
        ],
        "type": "KNOWLEDGE"
      },
      {
        "always_inject": false,
        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownWindhelmFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionWindhelm\")",
        "content": "Refugees' Rest is a memorial stone on the eastern road — marks where Dunmer refugees from the Red Year gathered after fleeing Morrowind, and where many of them died before reaching Windhelm.",
        "display_name": "Refugees' Rest",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.55,
        "knowledge_key": "dungeon.eastmarch.refugees_rest",
        "location": "",
        "tags": [
          "Refugees' Rest",
          "Eastmarch",
          "Dunmer",
          "memorial",
          "Red Year"
        ],
        "type": "KNOWLEDGE"
      },
      {
        "always_inject": false,
        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownWindhelmFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionWindhelm\")",
        "content": "Kynesgrove is the small settlement south of Windhelm built around the inn and the steam vents. The dragon mound above it is where Alduin first resurrected Sahloknir.",
        "display_name": "Kynesgrove - Sahloknir's Mound",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.85,
        "knowledge_key": "dungeon.eastmarch.kynesgrove",
        "location": "",
        "tags": [
          "Kynesgrove",
          "dragon mound",
          "Sahloknir",
          "Alduin",
          "Iddra",
          "Roggi"
        ],
        "type": "KNOWLEDGE"
      },
      {
        "always_inject": false,
        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownWindhelmFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionWindhelm\")",
        "content": "Witchmist Grove is a small wooded hollow east of Windhelm — a single hagraven called Moira lives in the cottage at its center, and few of the local children believe she's safe.",
        "display_name": "Witchmist Grove",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.65,
        "knowledge_key": "dungeon.eastmarch.witchmist_grove",
        "location": "",
        "tags": [
          "Witchmist Grove",
