        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownWindhelmFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionWindhelm\")",
        "content": "Darkwater Crossing is the small Stormcloak-aligned mining settlement in southern Eastmarch — also the place Ulfric and his soldiers were once captured by the Imperials before Helgen.",
